      <title>英国卡梅伦向中国外长提出红海和人权问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uks-cameron-raises-red-sea-human-rights-issues-with-chinese-counterpart-2024-02-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交部在一份声明中表示，英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦周五在慕尼黑安全会议上会见了中国外交部长王毅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uks-cameron-raises-red-sea-human-rights-issues-with-chinese-counterpart-2024-02-17/</guid>
